{"title":"三峡梦","authors":["梁上泉"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":3,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡梦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国人大代表　梁上泉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常到三峡游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不梦三峡？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥闻峡山回声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊望峡江浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛都在动情呼喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早建三峡大坝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古老的大盆地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本是个古老的大海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只因沉滞得太久太久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决然把重山切割开来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辟出了四百里三峡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死水才有鲜活的澎湃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高坝，筑在三斗坪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回水，漫没几多城？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屈原别祠，再次作游魂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张飞迁庙，同当新移民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淹了旧景，又添新景，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山鹰乐与江鸥为邻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三峡梦是个光明梦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦成现实，并不轻松，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造福子孙的惊天伟业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉重地落在我们手中。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美梦更圆，事更成功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠民主决策，科学驱动！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":2,"page_end":2}